title: A merry, not scary Halloween at the Zoo
text:
Published By: Louisville Courier-Journal: Lifestyle - Today 
Trick-or-treaters braved the rain Saturday night as Meijer presented “The World’s Largest Halloween Party!” at the Louisville Zoo.
